OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny spells for much of the
OL,6,FUK, however cloudier in the northeast
OL,7,Fwith bright spells developing here
OL,8,Flater. Dry for most, but a few showers
OL,9,Fpossible across the south. Hot in the
OL,10,Fsouthwest, but feeling a little
OL,11,Ffresher elsewhere.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FScattered showers and
OL,14,Fthunderstorms possibly moving north
OL,15,Facross England and Wales overnight.
OL,16,FOtherwise dry with clear spells, but
OL,17,Flow cloud returning in the northeast.
OL,18,FA cooler night than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
